descr: "A code system resource specifies a set of codes drawn from one or more code systems."

fields.name: code
fields.descr: "A code that is used to identify the property. The code is used internally (in CodeSystem.concept.property.code) and also externally, such as in property filters."

fields.name: uri
fields.descr: "Reference to the formal meaning of the property. One possible source of meaning is the [Concept Properties](codesystem-concept-properties.html) code system."

fields.name: description
fields.descr: "A description of the property- why it is defined, and how its value might be used."

fields.name: type
fields.descr: "The type of the property value. Properties of type \"code\" contain a code defined by the code system (e.g. a reference to anotherr defined concept)."
